GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Metaphor> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_Metaphor> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Metaphor> ;
    narr:childCount "53"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "6daa5aeb9823e809668e9c6eadbe96066ec6e9e9" ;
    narr:narration """This hub tracks the evolution of the system's rhetorical architecture, where technical domains—primarily physics, software engineering, and ophthalmology—are mapped onto cognitive and organizational processes. The foundational [steering-vector physics](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SteeringVector) and [flocking-behavior origin story](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FlockingPieceVerbatim) remain central, now extended through [archery and kinetic aim](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EVFlocking_ArrowMetaphor) to describe iterative convergence. The [optometrist metaphor](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_OptometristMetaphor) persists as the primary UX anchor, while [engineering-as-infrastructure](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_EngineeringMetaphor) metaphors—such as [Git-like versioning](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_GitMetaphor) and [OS-level program installation](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ModelAsOSMetaphor)—frame the product as a tool for managing organizational worldview. Recent additions introduce spatial and mechanical imagery, including [white-space collapse](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_WhiteSpaceCollapse) to describe output steering and [castle-security](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_CastleMetaphor) for IP disclosure. The corpus exhibits a consistent idiolect of physical-exertion metaphors, such as [mountain-climbing milestones](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Tranche1_MountainMetaphor), alongside a growing reliance on [technical primitives](narr:https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_SelfServe_TechnicalMetaphor) to describe abstract architectural decisions.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_CompilerSentenceQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_FlockingPieceVerbatim> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_ModelAsOSMetaphor> ;
